  <Contents>k__BackingField:
  - <wiggle><color=#FFD700>One thing before you start.</color></wiggle>
  - Every figure on those tracks is <color=#88FF88><b>worth something.</b></color>
    Or costs you. Or <shake>explodes.</shake>
  - <color=#C0C0C0><i>Position matters. Neighbors matter. Order matters.</i></color>
  - Check the <color=#FFD700><b>Book</b></color> if you need details.
  - <wiggle><color=#FF4444><b>Now stop reading and pull the lever.</b></color></wiggle>
